activate Controller
Controller -> SchedSvc : fetchJadwalKetersediaan(arenaId)
activate SchedSvc
SchedSvc -> DB : query jadwal ketersediaan
activate DB
DB --> SchedSvc : jadwal
deactivate DB
SchedSvc --> Controller : jadwal
deactivate SchedSvc
Controller --> App : tampilkan jadwal ketersediaan
deactivate Controller
deactivate App

